When the user asks for a status overview, repo table, or cross-repo summary, follow the procedure defined in `../haderach-platform/.cursor/rules/cross-repo-status.mdc`.

The status table covers **all** site repositories, not just this one. Always produce the full table regardless of which repo the request originates from.
